                <a href="/cic" class="flex items-center space-x-2 px-4 py-2 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 border border-purple-400/30 hover:border-purple-400/60 rounded-lg font-medium transition-all duration-200">
                    <span>‚Üê</span>
